column2: SELECT d.ra AS input_ra, d.dec AS input_dec, s.ra as s_ra, s.dec as s_dec, s.z as s_z, s.specObjID as s_specObjID, e.specObjID as e_specObjID, s.sciencePrimary, m.* into mydb.MyTable_# from MyDB.CAGN_strict_radec AS d OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (d.ra, d.dec, #) AS n LEFT JOIN SpecObjAll AS s ON n.objid = s.bestObjID LEFT JOIN emissionLinesPort AS e ON s.specObjID = e.specObjID LEFT JOIN stellarMassStarFormingPort AS m ON m.specObjID = s.specObjID
